title: everything is a mess and that’s ok
itunes:title: everything is a mess and that’s ok
description:
Brooke and Danielle are together today discussing how the state of the world right now has truly left everything as a mess.  The two give advice on loneliness, not having a “plan” and read listener submissions on advice and tactics on how to handle all of this craziness going on.
